# Expo SDK 56+ made expo/fetch the default global fetch. Its multipart
# FormData file-part handling is broken as of this SDK (throws
# "Unsupported FormDataPart implementation" — expo/expo#33134), which breaks
# our profile photo / document uploads in deliveryApi.ts. Opt back into
# React Native's classic fetch until that's fixed upstream.
EXPO_PUBLIC_USE_RN_FETCH=1
